name: Wild Woodland
description: This is the collection of wood prints that i did for my final negotiated brief and final year show, all these wood cuts are part of a set which together exhibit my interest in ecology and entomology .The wood cuts are priced at £50 for one and £300 for the set.

name: Three insects
description: These insects were made in the same way as the wild woodland set but are different i put them on a different type of wood so they were a completely different series £7 each or £20 for the set.

name: Stickers
description: There are three designs all printed on 10 cm gloss vinyl, is thick and really durable so they are good for anything, they were made as a promo' for me and my work but i think they are better than that its the skulls of a fox, goose and deer .I chose these three because of they way in which they are hunted all for sport .I also added my name in my own typeface i hope you like them .The sale is for a set of 3.

name: Postcards
description: These postcards are all different sizes They were all screen printed by me and i also added a postcard style back, you can buy the collection for £10 and that includes a handmade envelope and band.

name: Pencil cases
description: These pencil cases were made by me by hand, hand screen printed, hand sewn and illustrated .They differ slightly in size but they all comfortably fit pens and pencils i hope you enjoy them, i also created two pin cushions with these designs, they are also available enquire within :)
